WEBVTT

1
00:05:09.060 --> 00:05:12.100 
给我来点番茄酱吧
Squeeze a little more ketchup on it, would you, buddy?

2
00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:14.770 
但如果你矜持点冷静点
However, if you hang back and stay cool...

3
00:05:14.940 --> 00:05:17.110 
女孩就会给你自动送上门
...the women come to you.

4
00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:20.900 
当然我不是在指"你"  不过  你应该明白我的理论了
Well, not to you specifically, but you get the theory.

5
00:05:21.070 --> 00:05:23.450 
是啊  我又不蠢  只是理论上是个父亲
Yeah, I'm not stupid. Just physically repellent...

6
00:05:23.610 --> 00:05:25.660 
又不懂得如何去爱
...and inherently unlovable.

7
00:05:25.820 --> 00:05:28.780 
别跟我抬杠  我是想教你点经验
Don't get snippy with me. I'm trying to teach you something.

8
00:05:28.950 --> 00:05:31.580 
我想要这一整个
Hey, I agreed to one.

9
00:05:31.750 --> 00:05:34.790 
杰克  如果你吃完饭了 干吗不开始做点作业
If you're finished with dinner, get started on homework.

10
00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:37.170 
我还饿着呢  他吃光了我的薯条
I'm still hungry.  He ate all my fries.

11
00:05:37.330 --> 00:05:40.050 
你做完作业可以吃点冰激凌
You can have ice cream when you've done your homework.

